::Prowl/Annihilator/Killer::

Annihilator grins evily as he sees Iron Raptor's tail coming at him. He 
dives, leaving the tail swinging straight into Prowl.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl grunts as he is smashed into a tree by Iron Raptor's tail.

He shakes his head, sitting up on the tree only to see Annihilator smash his 
fist into the maximal's face, sending Prowl flying back through the tree.

The maximal does not have enough time to respond to Tritan's question as 
Annihilator shoots him in the stomach.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killer lets out a breath as Iron Raptor turns away from him. He pulls out his 
rifle, jumping back and firing at her.
